Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:57.12,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(120,120)}夢中に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:03:04.04,OP1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be8\fad(120,120)}崩れた感情の果てに
