Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切迎来终结之日的前一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.48,0:00:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无心睡眠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 永
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.92,0:00:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！ 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.79,0:01:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.29,0:01:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.92,0:01:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到没
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.46,0:01:25.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要打倒<丧尸>
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有把头爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.94,0:01:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽 永
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.51,0:01:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧 来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.73,0:01:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.78,0:01:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.08,0:01:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}到底是怎么回事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:37.98,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(350,260)\fs22\fry1\frz-20.5\bord0\c&H0F0F0F&\}未经许可严禁私自进入校园 有事请联系办公室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Goose
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Goose
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来当阿孝的新娘子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.79,0:03:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？ 你是说真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 拉勾上吊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么留级了 明明是尖子生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿孝你不懂的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.71,0:04:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又分到一个班了 多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉勾上吊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.04,0:04:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说谎的人要吞千根针
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你傻嘛你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高城
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一碰到烦心事 总是跑到同一个地方蹲着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说 一学期开始就这个状态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说补习 到时留级也有可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第五堂课还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是天才 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟碰运气混进来的小室是不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高城 我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么总是找我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我讨厌笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且特讨厌不肯承认自己是笨蛋的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:05:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少你是个知道自己是笨蛋的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你笨的地方 说不定能去掉一点傻气啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 不就是被青梅竹马甩了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我以前 真的对阿孝有过那种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你好像没有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以又如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那人搞什么 可疑人物？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要乱搞事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 林老师 交给我处理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:05:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 手岛老师 不能过分使用暴力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.29,0:06:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手岛老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血止不住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死…死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.77,0:06:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样 仅仅这点伤就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手岛老师 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手岛老师 太好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小室 你翘课也就算了 现在还妨碍同学们上课
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.72,0:07:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来 我们快走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:07.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在校门被杀了 情况很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.77,0:07:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你能有什么得益
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底怎么了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:21.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你脑子里到底在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话 听我的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,校门口有人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,体育教师过去看情况 结果出了事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在老师们在自相残杀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 忘记拿东西了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.85,0:07:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你说的是真的 我们需要武器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:51.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给 丽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.33,0:07:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看我这样 空手道可是考到级的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 我们离开学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先叫警察吧 爸爸也在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,违反校规也是有用武之时的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:12.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您继续等待 或者过后再拨打一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在110因呼叫过于集中 线路繁忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:28.02,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,请您继续等待 或者过后再拨打一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,110竟然爆满 怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.56,0:08:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向全校同学通报
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在校内正发生暴力事件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同学们请按照老师的指示前往避难
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:42.90,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,重复一遍 现在校内正发生暴力事件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于发觉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.31,0:08:45.34,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,同学们请按照老师们的指示…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.97,0:08:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高城
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.22,0:09:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘 我们开溜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.76,0:09:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要不要 滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.51,0:09:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是要逃去外边么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教学楼的人都满了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们跑去管理栋那边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永是对的 听他的话就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…教现代语文的胁坂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点 那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.69,0:10:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 别靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插他 丽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用留手 认真上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.43,0:10:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别瞧不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长枪术部！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 明明刺中了心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么还能动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.09,0:11:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽 趁现在快拔出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永 快离开他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种家伙 干不过我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太扯了 为什么这家伙 会有这么大力气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 快离开永
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:30.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么不离开他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.60,0:11:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.15,0:11:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明死了却还在动啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿孝 快救他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快…快想办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是被他咬掉了点肉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 别咬我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些怪物一起上的话 战不过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去屋顶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屋顶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们据守在那 等救援过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.86,0:12:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里有天文台
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才还是跟往常一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.23,0:13:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑鹰直升机？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美军？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是自卫队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是从哪里来的 附近没有驻扎地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.14,0:13:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在附近驻扎的自卫队 不会毫无理由就飞过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是接到了特殊任务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有功夫救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算看到了那情形都不管
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连在可以四处逃跑的外头都那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:38.81,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,来人救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.22,0:13:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,校舍里面现在肯定…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们俩一起逃跑的话肯定没问题的 美铃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 我们永远都是好朋友啊 敏美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:56.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.51,0:13:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救我 救我啊 美铃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫你放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.38,0:14:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦 没错 是噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得去学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.86,0:14:33.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要狠狠敲诈新入部学生一笔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是类似病毒的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.76,0:14:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,<丧尸>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,<丧尸>？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算死人向我们袭来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟这不是电影或游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以叫他们做<丧尸>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.84,0:14:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,<丧尸>会吃人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被吃的人死了 会复活并成为<丧尸>的一份子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:14:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道是什么原因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.74,0:15:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了爆头 就没有其他方法能干掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.77,0:15:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上那里去 封住楼梯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！ 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定事出有因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要查清楚原因 就能找到解决方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天文台有没有打火机或者火柴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:15:58.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们找找
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得趁现在点着火种
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.49,0:16:03.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到晚上 <丧尸>的行动就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:10.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿孝 永他…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是被咬了一下 为什么会这么严重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟电影一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要被咬到就没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.03,0:16:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像电影那样的事 是绝对不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周围都跟电影一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿孝 能不能帮我个忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.27,0:16:59.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的话 应该能直接掉到地面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计撞到地面的冲击可以把头爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.92,0:17:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:18.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想变成<丧尸>！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.76,0:17:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿孝 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.81,0:17:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想到最后 都保持自我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.91,0:17:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要死啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:37.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离他远点 丽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 你不能这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会的 永才不会变成<丧尸>呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永是特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.93,0:18:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:19:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 阿孝 永怎么会死呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.48,0:19:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一定是骗人的 骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确很扯淡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢之极
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.06,0:19:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.31,0:19:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是事实！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不动手的话 你已经被咬了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.45,0:21:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本不想你救我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.99,0:21:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想见到…永这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.72,0:21:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要这样苟活的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我宁愿被永咬 成为<丧尸>的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.84,0:21:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永不希望那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.25,0:21:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿孝你懂什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.89,0:21:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.54,0:21:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实阿孝 你很讨厌永吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:21:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他跟我在交往
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.16,0:22:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.48,0:22:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.63,0:22:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在的话只会碍眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.04,0:22:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下去干<丧尸>
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.02,0:22:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.57,0:22:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人能有什么作为
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.70,0:22:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.40,0:22:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿孝…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.87,0:22:31.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 那些话不是真心的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是说气话罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你 求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.15,0:22:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我… 跟我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.65,0:23:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切迎来终结之日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.45,0:23:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 对好朋友下了杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.94,0:23:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次抱住了曾经喜欢的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.73,0:23:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}你应该知道被咬到的人的下场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.60,0:23:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}我想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.45,0:23:30.03,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不太懂 但我悟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.06,0:23:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}爸爸 你没听到我的声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.03,0:23:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.69,0:23:32.80,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服跟性命 哪样重要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}保住男人的尊严 是女人的矜持
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(353,430)\fs20}Style
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.91,0:23:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}别…别过来！
